name: CELEBRATE SALAMANCA - BLUE
description:
One of the best known tourist destinations in the state, this is a hive of market activity, coffee drinking, gallery perusing and the all important chess playing. Throw in a few fish and a big orange boat and what have you got? Why Salamanca!

100% Indian cotton tea towel

Available in two colourways - chartreuse and blue

Created in Tasmania by Cathy McAuliffe and Jen Murnaghan -  a cracking collaboration...

This item will be dispatched within 2 days and shipped via Australia Post. Please allow an additional 3-5 days for delivery.

name: TASMANIA HOW DO I LOVE THEE - VALUE 3 PACK TEA TOWELS
description:
Let me count the ways... Or so the poet Elizabeth Barrett Browning once said. But you know, you REALLY do love this island and the words describing this state are all yours.  A few months ago we asked you to describe this state. This tea towel bears the fruit. Now go forth, dry those dishes with pride! 

Pack of three available - this includes blue, gold and pink, a winning combination don't you think?

Dish Pig is designed and printed in Australia using 100% Indian Cotton. Wash in cold water, show off in your kitchen and if you're like me, use only on special occasions.

This item will be dispatched within 2 days and shipped via Australia Post. Please allow an additional 3-5 days for delivery.

name: Hobart Triptych - Custom Orders
description:
Created for the Spacebar Gallery All Around exhibition in March 2012, three needlework hoops hold Hobart together. 

Embroidered with love and attention, my love for geometry contrasts with the circular hoops and my passion for colour, is right there, ready to pop and party.

For custom orders using Hobart or any other place name on the Dish Pig tea towels, please contact me directly jen@dishpig.net

Please note, production can take up to 6 weeks.
